Beautiful, beautiful!
That's a wrap, folks!

37:52.662 --> 37:54.271
(applause, cheering)

37:54.439 --> 37:57.732
-Great job, everyone!
-(indistinct chatter)

37:59.836 --> 38:01.778
(crickets chirping)

38:02.005 --> 38:03.763
-(fire crackling)
-Oh. Thank you.

38:03.857 --> 38:05.173
(chuckles softly)

38:05.191 --> 38:06.524
A little late, Albie.

38:06.676 --> 38:09.010
What's so important
that it couldn't wait?

38:09.103 --> 38:10.453
Sit down, Nell.

38:16.536 --> 38:19.713
You and Dot
were thick as thieves.

38:20.966 --> 38:23.049
All right.

38:24.136 --> 38:25.802
Dottie said something
fore she passed.

38:25.953 --> 38:28.471
She said
that she'd done something.

38:28.623 --> 38:29.864
Something...

38:29.883 --> 38:31.624
that was unforgivable.

38:31.643 --> 38:33.626
Well, it<i> was</i> Dottie.

38:33.645 --> 38:36.146
We might want
to narrow that down a touch.

38:36.373 --> 38:37.372
Nellie.

38:37.541 --> 38:39.057
Think.

38:39.300 --> 38:41.151
This is important.

38:42.821 --> 38:43.820
(sighs)
You know...

38:44.047 --> 38:44.970
(sighs)

38:45.139 --> 38:46.972
She swore me to secrecy.

38:47.141 --> 38:50.327
A sister's loyalty
survives death.

38:50.403 --> 38:52.329
You live rent-free
on my property.

38:52.556 --> 38:55.165
You got loyalty to me, too,
Nell.

39:01.565 --> 39:06.009
You remember that barn fire
40 or so years ago?

39:06.160 --> 39:08.903
Yeah, I was on tour.
It burned to the ground.

39:08.922 --> 39:11.014
And...

39:11.165 --> 39:13.091
and you were told that Rosa,

39:13.185 --> 39:14.576
your lady friend,

39:14.594 --> 39:16.603
caused that fire...

39:17.764 --> 39:19.171
...and ran off

39:19.265 --> 39:21.583
so she wouldn't be blamed.

39:21.601 --> 39:22.600
That's right.

39:22.752 --> 39:24.694
Because that was Dottie's story.

39:24.846 --> 39:25.937
And no one questioned her.

39:26.106 --> 39:29.181
But let me ask you this.

39:29.275 --> 39:33.761
How do you think
Dottie's horses got out safe?

39:33.780 --> 39:35.538
Ahead of time?

39:41.195 --> 39:42.270
(distorted yelling)

39:42.363 --> 39:43.546
♪ ♪

39:47.201 --> 39:49.427
Rosa didn't cause that fire.

39:51.873 --> 39:54.265
And she didn't run off.

39:56.210 --> 39:58.019
(distorted yelling)

39:59.231 --> 40:01.231
♪ ♪

40:04.403 --> 40:06.277
(screaming)

40:07.739 --> 40:10.407
♪ ♪

40:19.901 --> 40:22.460
She died in that fire.

40:24.756 --> 40:26.906
Just as Dottie intended.

40:27.000 --> 40:28.925
No. No.

40:29.002 --> 40:30.652
No, she wouldn't have.

40:30.670 --> 40:33.412
Lord knows she had a temper,
but come on, Nell.

40:33.432 --> 40:36.991
She saw Rosa as a threat
to your future together.

40:37.010 --> 40:38.435
Your family.

40:38.586 --> 40:41.253
The dynasty she was building.

40:41.273 --> 40:43.273
She didn't have to worry.

40:44.334 --> 40:46.985
Rosa wasn't a threat
to anything.

40:48.930 --> 40:51.531
Well, Dottie didn't like
to take chances.

40:57.864 --> 41:00.039
Good night.

41:01.201 --> 41:04.127
(door opens, closes)

41:17.367 --> 41:19.867
-So, what now?
-(sighs)

41:19.961 --> 41:22.145
Daddy.

41:22.964 --> 41:24.814
Go inside.

41:24.966 --> 41:27.132
Hug your babies.

41:27.152 --> 41:29.393
Try to get some sleep.

41:29.546 --> 41:31.729
And the rest...

41:31.881 --> 41:34.532
is tomorrow's problem.

41:36.978 --> 41:38.995
(exhales)

41:43.651 --> 41:47.128
♪ ♪

42:03.429 --> 42:05.396
♪ ♪

42:22.432 --> 42:24.332
