42:30.456 --> 42:31.381
Hey.

42:31.532 --> 42:32.865
Ace?

42:32.884 --> 42:34.776
Hey, what are you...

42:34.794 --> 42:36.052
what are you doing?

42:42.727 --> 42:44.352
I saw it all.

